headline: Texas to investigate General Mills cereals over ‘healthy’ claims
summary: The Attorney General’s office has issued a civil investigative demand (CID) to General Mills, which sells cereals such as Trix and Lucky Charms.

headline: A Look Back at Shelf-Stable Food Stocks’ Q1 Earnings: Utz (NYSE:UTZ) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at shelf-stable food stocks, starting with Utz (NYSE:UTZ).
